creator: Far Mills
descriptionHtml:
“Anna’s Adventure” is a beautifully designed hidden objects game, which will send you into a mysterious magical world. You will go on an unforgettable journey searching for magical items, unraveling mysteries and creating magical spells.

In this fairy world you can find items and use them to create spells to rescue your new friends. Complete harder tasks and make stronger potions to develop your skills and become a powerful magician.

Save the mysterious world. Fight the black magic that has taken hold of the beautiful kingdom. Assemble a collection of magical items to create a powerful spell. Use it to free anybody who was conquered by the sly and treacherous villain, whose lies had seized all magic.

Become a wizard and compete with your friends to show who is the best.

title: Anna’s Adventure Hidden Object

creator: Far Mills
descriptionHtml:
Anna's Adventure is a beautiful Hidden Object game that takes you on an exciting journey through the mysterious world of magic. In this mystery adventure, you will seek and find hidden objects, solve different puzzles, decorate a fairy world, and plant and harvest magical plants.

Search and collect items in this unforgettable journey to create magic potions, witch amulets, and mystery talismans. Use secret spells in this fairy world, to rescue your new friends and develop your magic skills, became a powerful magician.

Improves your detective skills to unveil a hidden family secret. Find a secret spy that has taken hold of the beautiful and mysterious world. Solve riddles and compete with friends to show who is the best detective wizard in this journey.

Features of this adventure game:

Enjoy great graphics, and seek and find hidden items in various search scenes using witch tools. Play different modes in hidden object scenes to build your visual memory in this mystery adventure.

Open new chapters of the thrilling story to help Anna unravel the mystery of the past. Use your detective skills to reveal the secrets that the fairy world hides and return magic in the kingdom!

Rescue the characters from the curse and their magic will help you in Hidden Object scenes. Find and collect pieces of puzzles for open mystery stories about the past of characters.

Enjoy witch magic to plant flowers, grow crystals, and harvest beehives. Create fairy talismans, weave witch amulets and brew magical potions from your harvest.

Look into the crystal ball to see the secrets of the future. Become a fortune teller to get a prediction in this unsolved mystery adventure game and share this prediction with your friends.

Practice with witch abilities to renovate and decorate this full of secrets and mysterious world to your taste.

This hidden object game is free. But additional bonuses can be unlocked via in-app purchases.
